ut\", \"connection error\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"10.233.55.4:50051\",\n      \"reason\": \"目标服务连接超时，可能是网络问题或服务不可用\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的指标数据，我对故障期间的系统异常进行了分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标显著飙升，响应时间从正常114643.5ms急剧增加到20069121.0ms，变化率197.73%，表明该Pod存在严重性能瓶颈\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 114643.5 → 20069121.0 (变化率197.73%), rrt: 4363.68 → 681880.36 (变化率197.46%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标异常升高，同时error_ratio和server_error_ratio从0%上升到32%，表明前端服务存在响应延迟和服务器错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 150656.5 → 20065808.0 (变化率197.02%), rrt: 8670.85 → 138813.58 (变化率176.48%), error_ratio: 0.0 → 0.32\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标显著恶化，error_ratio和server_error_ratio从0%上升到28%，响应时间性能严重下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 161063.5 → 20064840.0 (变化率196.81%), rrt: 8806.92 → 119300.27 (变化率172.5%), error_ratio: 0.0 → 0.28\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标异常，error_ratio和server_error_ratio出现峰值，P99响应时间急剧增加196.89%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max P99: 157229.0 → 20044391.0 (变化率196.89%), rrt P99: 9636.28 → 429346.88 (变化率191.22%), error_ratio P99: 0.0 → 1.05\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio和client_error_ratio的P99值从0%飙升到46.15%，表明该服务出现大量客户端错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio P99: 0.0 → 46.15%, client_error_ratio P99: 0.0 → 46.15%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio和client_er